s drawn as the winning set.  Suppose a subset of <span class=3D"texhtml mva=
r" style=3D"font-style:italic;">T</span>&nbsp;balls (such as <span class=3D=
"texhtml"><i>T</i> =3D 6</span>) is selected on a lottery ticket.  Suppose =
